thread.title: Wendy Momsen
thread.title_full: California Casualty Auto and Home Insurance reviewed by Wendy Momsen

author: Wendy Momsen
title: Wendy Momsen
text: I have had both home and auto insurance with California Casualty for about 5 years now. They are always very helpful when I call with a change or a question. I haven't had any claims in the time that I have been with them so I can't give any feedback on that process.
